quran[27{c,v,t}:
37,25,tum kokiya howa ke aik dosray ki madad nahi karte ?
37,26,balkay aaj to woh farmanbardar hain
37,27,aur aik dosray ki taraf rukh karkay sawal ( o jawab ) karen ge
37,28,kahin gekiya tum hi hamaray paas dayen ( aur baen ) se atay they
37,29,woh kahin ge balkay tum hi imaan laane walay nah they
37,30,aur hamara tum par kuch zor nah tha. balkay tum sarkash log they
37,31,so hamaray baray mein hamaray perwar-digaar ki baat poori hogayi ab hum mazay chakhain ge
37,32,hum ne tum ko bhi gumraahkiya ( aur ) hum khud bhi gumraah they
37,33,pas woh is roz azaab mein aik dosray ke shareek hon ge
37,34,hum gunahgaaron ke sath aisa hikiya karte hain
37,35,un ka yeh haal tha ke jab un se kaha jata tha ke khuda ke siwa koi mabood nahi to ghuroor karte they
37,36,aur kehte they ke bhala hum aik deewany shayar ke kehnay se kahin apne mabodon ko chore dainay walay hain
37,37,balkay woh haq le kar aeye hain aur ( pehlay ) payghambaroon ko sacha kehte hain
37,38,be shak tum takleef dainay walay azaab ka maza chakhnay walay ho
37,39,aur tum ko badla waisa hi miley ga jaisay tum kaam karte they
37,40,magar jo khuda ke bandgaan khaas hain
37,41,yahi log hain jin ke liye rozi muqarrar hai
37,42,( yani ) meway aur un ka aizazkiya jaye ga
37,43,Nemat ke baghoon mein
37,44,aik dosray ke samnay takhton par ( baithy hon ge )
37,45,sharaab lateef ke jaam ka un mein daur chal raha hoga
37,46,jo rang ki safaid aur peenay walon ke liye ( sara sar ) lazzat hogi
37,47,nah is se drdِ sir ho aur nah woh is se matawaale hon ge
37,48,aur un ke paas aurtain hon gi jo nigehain neechi rakhti hon gi aur ankhen barri barri
37,49,goya woh mehfooz anday hain
37,50,phir woh aik dosray ki taraf rukh karkay sawal (o jawab ) karen ge
37,51,aik kehnay wala un mein se kahe ga ke mera aik hum nasheen tha
